articles.description: "We must protect against the predatory use of AI to steal professional artists' voices and likenesses, violate creators' rights, and destroy the music ecosystem," reads an open letter from the Artist Rights Alliance
articles.content:
A group of over 200 artists has come together to sign an open letter urging tech companies to "stop devaluing music" and cease the use of artificial intelligence to infringe on artists' rights.
